$interpreted: Nikola: Right here!
Rune: A pond of lights?
Nikola: The construction of the entire New City was based around Rune patterns. These lights are the center of the Rune.
Nikola: All we need to do is destroy this and we can stop Devious!
Soldier: More are coming...
Soldier: Oh...you must be...the tattooed fellow...
Rune: ...Do you know me?
Soldier: General Lazer...knew that you'd be here...he said...if you want to save your friend...don't mess around...
Rune: Sanchez and Elio, where are they?
Soldier: In the plaza of the New City...
Soldier: If you do anything to mess up the Blessing Ceremony, they will both be executed immediately...
Nikola: If the Rune is activated, many more will die! We must first destroy this place!
Rune: No. I must save...Sanchez and Elio.
Soldier: You really are an idiot. Going up against Lazer is basically asking to be killed...
Nikola: It was difficult as all hell to set all this up. So the simple-minded folk turned out to be the hardest to control...?
Clark: Maria, put me down! Do you hear me? Maria!
Maria: Find~~~Sophie~~~
Clark: Ouch...at least we finally stopped.
Maria: C-C-Clark, find Sophie.
Clark: No, not find Sophie. We've got to bring Rune back and then find Sophie. We don't even know where Sophie is.
Maria: S-S-S-Sophie.
Clark: I already told you. We don't know where Sophie is...
Clark: Here!?
Clark: H-Headmaster Ceres!
Sophie: Didn't I say we'd meet up at the market? Why are you here? Where's Rune?
Clark: Umm...
Rune: Where are Sanchez and Elio!?
Lazer: Hmph, I'm wondering that myself.
Lazer: If you could only save one of them, who would you choose?
Rune: Both!
Lazer: Not all things can go as you would like. I'll ask you again. Who would you save?
Rune: Both!
Lazer: I see you're quite stubborn. Since that's the case, I'll choose for you.
Rune: Sanchez!
Sanchez: ...ugh...oh...
Rune: Sanchez...are you okay?
Sanchez: Ya piece of trash! Who told you to come here? Fool! It's a trap...
Lazer: Sorry. Although I asked you to choose, I never planned on letting any of you go.
Sanchez: Get out of here! Don't worry about me!
Rune: We go...together.
Sanchez: Did you forget what that chameleon just said? Not everything can go as you would like.
Lazer: That's right. Bringing along this nuisance, there's no way you can defeat this many people.
Lazer: Especially not me.
Sanchez: ...Damn...
Rune: We go...together.
Sanchez: Idiot! Do you have fricking ears or what!?
Lazer: ...Excellent. I've no right to speak of this.
Lazer: Becoming a fool, all for one person. You and I actually have many things in common. It's really...
Lazer: ——quite a SHAME!!!!!
Rune: San...chez...?
Sanchez: ...That move...is too...sinister...hmph...unless the big bad...Sanchez...blocks it....*cough*...!
Rune: Sanchez!
Rune: Nikola!
Nikola: Thank me later. Let's split up and get out of here.
Nikola: Remember. No matter what, stay alive. We'll meet at the Snake Bone Shrine.
Lazer: ...Who is that...?
Scout: General.
Lazer: Something is happening on the border?
Scout: Yes, sir. The ones you told us to keep an eye on...
Lazer: They've returned...?
Scout: General, what should we do next?
Lazer: Tell all units. Begin sniping immediately.
Scout: Yes, sir.
Lazer: ——He's the only one that's left.
